Description :
        Released in 2006 to celebrate Kochikame's 30th Anniversary, this special edition volume contains several pages of information and pictures related to Kochikame.The volume also contains many crossover drawings from other authors, an omake about an interview with the author of Kochikame, and 5 crossover chapters with other famous JUMP series.1.
